<h1>QR Codes</h1>
These can be slow so please be patient.  Each link will display 24 codes.<br/>
<br/>
<p>
	<%= link_to "Generate New QR Codes in PDF", url_for(:action => :print_new_codes, :format => :pdf), :target => '_blank' %>
</p>
<p>
	<%= link_to "Generate New QR Codes in HTML", url_for(:action => :print_new_codes), :target => '_blank' %>
</p>

